%% Data Science Pipelines - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / SDK
    participant API as ml-pipeline API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflows<br/>Execution Engine
    participant Driver as kfp-driver<br/>Init Container
    participant Launcher as kfp-launcher<br/>Sidecar
    participant UserContainer as User Container
    participant S3 as MinIO / S3<br/>9000/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as MySQL / PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432/TCP
    participant MetaGRPC as metadata-grpc-server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant MetaWriter as metadata-writer<br/>Python Agent
    participant PA as persistence-agent
    participant SWC as scheduledworkflow<br/>Controller
    participant Cache as cache-server<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Execution (V2 Architecture)
        User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>Auth: kubeflow-userid header
        API->>DB: Store run metadata<br/>Username/Password
        API->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>ServiceAccount token
        K8s->>Argo: Schedule Workflow
        Argo->>Driver: Execute init container
        Driver->>API: Resolve inputs (gRPC/8887)<br/>ServiceAccount token
        Driver->>S3: Fetch artifacts<br/>AccessKey/SecretKey
        Driver->>Launcher: Pass resolved inputs
        Launcher->>UserContainer: Launch user code
        UserContainer-->>Launcher: Output artifacts
        Launcher->>S3: Store artifacts<br/>AccessKey/SecretKey
        MetaWriter->>MetaGRPC: Write execution metadata<br/>gRPC (plaintext)
        PA->>API: Report workflow status<br/>gRPC/8887
        API-->>User: Run status response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over User,SWC: Flow 2: Recurring Pipeline Execution
        User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/recurringruns<br/>Auth: kubeflow-userid header
        API->>K8s: Create ScheduledWorkflow CR<br/>ServiceAccount token
        SWC->>K8s: Watch ScheduledWorkflow CRs<br/>ServiceAccount token
        SWC->>API: Create Run (gRPC/8887)<br/>ServiceAccount token
        SWC->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>ServiceAccount token
    end

    rect rgb(245, 255, 230)
        Note over K8s,Cache: Flow 3: Pipeline Step Caching
        K8s->>Cache: Pod admission webhook<br/>HTTPS/443 (mTLS)
        Cache->>DB: Check cache key<br/>Username/Password
        Cache-->>K8s: Mutate pod (inject cached result)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 245)
        Note over User,S3: Flow 4: UI Artifact Viewing
        User->>API: GET /pipeline (via Route)<br/>TLS edge termination
        Note right of API: Proxied through ml-pipeline-ui (3000/TCP)
        API->>S3: Retrieve artifacts<br/>AccessKey/SecretKey
        API-->>User: Rendered artifacts
    end
